Math.tex: a\Ydown b\quad a\Yleft b\quad a\Yright b\quad a\Yup b
Math.text: formulae@(a Ydown b, formulae@(a Yleft b, formulae@(a Yright b, a Yup b)))

Math.tex: a\baro b\quad a\bbslash b\quad a\binampersand b\quad a\bindnasrepma b
Math.text: formulae@(a apl-reversal b, formulae@(a bbslash b, formulae@(a additive-conjunction b, a multiplicative-disjunction b)))

Math.tex: a\boxast b\quad a\boxbar b\quad a\boxbox b\quad a\boxbslash b\quad a\boxcircle b% \quad a\boxdot b\quad a\boxempty b\quad a\boxslash b
Math.text: formulae@(list@(boxast@(a, b), a) boxbar b, list@(boxbox@(a, b), boxbslash@(a, b), boxcircle@(a, b), a boxdot b, a) boxempty b, boxslash@(a, b))

Math.tex: a\curlyveedownarrow b\quad a\curlyveeuparrow b\quad a\curlywedgedownarrow b% \quad a\curlywedgeuparrow b
Math.text: formulae@(a curlyveedownarrow b, formulae@(a curlyveeuparrow b, formulae@(a curlywedgedownarrow b, a curlywedgeuparrow b)))

Math.tex: a\fatbslash b\quad a\fatsemi b\quad a\fatslash b\quad a\interleave b
Math.text: formulae@(a fatbslash b, formulae@(a fatsemi b, formulae@(a fatslash b, a interleave b)))

Math.tex: a\leftslice b\quad a\merge b\quad a\minuso b\quad a\moo b\quad a\nplus b
Math.text: formulae@(a leftslice b, formulae@(a merge b, a minuso list@(b, a * moo * b, a intersection-plus b)))

Math.tex: a\obar b\quad a\oblong b\quad a\obslash b\quad a\ogreaterthan b\quad a% \olessthan b\quad a\ovee b\quad a\owedge b
Math.text: formulae@(a obar b, formulae@(a oblong b, formulae@(a obslash b, formulae@(a ogreaterthan b, formulae@(a olessthan b, formulae@(a ovee b, a owedge b))))))

Math.tex: a\rightslice b\quad a\sslash b\quad a\talloblong b\quad a\varbigcirc b\quad a% \varcurlyvee b\quad a\varcurlywedge b
Math.text: formulae@(a rightslice b, formulae@(a sslash b, formulae@(a talloblong list@(b, a varbigcirc b), formulae@(a varcurlyvee b, a varcurlywedge b))))

Math.tex: a\varoast b\quad a\varobar b\quad a\varobslash b\quad a\varocircle b\quad a% \varodot b\quad a\varogreaterthan b\quad a\varolessthan b
Math.text: formulae@(list@(a varoast b, a) varobar b, list@(a varobslash b, a varocircle b, a varodot b, a) varogreaterthan b, a varolessthan b)

Math.tex: a\varominus b\quad a\varoplus b\quad a\varoslash b\quad a\varotimes b\quad a% \varovee b\quad a\varowedge b\quad a\vartimes b
Math.text: formulae@(list@(a varominus b, a additive-disjunction b, a) varoslash b, list@(a multiplicative-conjunction b, a) varovee b, a varowedge list@(b, a vartimes b))
list@(bigbox, bigcurlywedge, bigcurlyvee, biginterleave, intersection-plus, bigparallel, bigsqcap, bigtriangledown, bigtriangleup)
list@(bigbox, bigcurlywedge, bigcurlyvee, biginterleave, intersection-plus, bigparallel, bigsqcap, bigtriangledown, bigtriangleup)
list@(intersection-plus, intersection-plus, intersection-plus, intersection-plus)
list@(inplus, niplus, ntrianglelefteqslant, ntrianglerighteqslant, trianglelefteqslant, trianglerighteqslant)

Math.tex: a\subsetplus b\quad a\subsetpluseq b\quad a\supsetplus b\quad a\supsetpluseq b
Math.text: formulae@(a subset-plus b, formulae@(a subset-equals-plus b, formulae@(a superset-plus b, a superset-equals-plus b)))

Math.tex: a\mapsfromchar b\quad a\mapsfrom b\quad a\Mapsfromchar b\quad a\Mapsfrom b% \quad a\longmapsfrom b\quad a\Longmapsfrom b\quad
Math.text: formulae@(a mapsfromchar b, formulae@(a mapsfrom b, formulae@(a Mapsfromchar b, formulae@(a Mapsfrom b, formulae@(a longmapsfrom b, a Longmapsfrom b)))))

Math.tex: a\Mapstochar b\quad a\Mapsto b\quad a\Longmapsto b\quad
Math.text: formulae@(a Mapstochar b, formulae@(a Mapsto b, a Longmapsto b))

Math.tex: a\nnearrow b\quad a\nnwarrow b\quad a\ssearrow b\quad a\sswarrow b
Math.text: formulae@(a nnearrow b, formulae@(a nnwarrow b, formulae@(a ssearrow b, a sswarrow b)))

Math.tex: a\leftarrowtriangle b\quad a\rightarrowtriangle b\quad a% \leftrightarrowtriangle b\quad a\leftrightarroweq b\quad a\lightning b
Math.text: formulae@(a leftarrowtriangle b, formulae@(a rightarrowtriangle b, formulae@(a leftrightarrowtriangle b, formulae@(a leftrightarroweq b, a lightning b))))

Math.tex: a\shortdownarrow b\quad a\shortleftarrow b\quad a\shortrightarrow b\quad a\shortuparrow b
Math.text: formulae@(a shortdownarrow b, formulae@(a shortleftarrow b, formulae@(a shortrightarrow b, a shortuparrow b)))

Math.tex: a\arrownot b\quad a\longarrownot b\quad a\Arrownot b\quad a\Longarrownot b
Math.text: formulae@(a arrownot b, formulae@(a longarrownot b, formulae@(a Arrownot b, a Longarrownot b)))
